    <h1>About Molave</h1>
    <p>Molave, Zamboanga del Sur, has a rich history dating back to the Subanen tribe and its subsequent settlement by other families. It became a municipality in 1948, with its vibrant commerce making it a commercial hub in the region.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="services">
  <div class="container">
